Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.59,0:00:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.14,0:00:09.22,Title 3,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,414)}"The Mushroom Pile Is Served"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.49,0:00:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.40,0:00:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The ready-made dinner is complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.38,0:00:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Now all that's left is to wait for Nikaido to return!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.36,0:00:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez! The hell is she doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.02,0:00:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Calm down... I don't need to win here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.75,0:00:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Let's have some more fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.83,0:00:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,My eye...! Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.93,0:00:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! Let's fight some more...! Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.52,0:01:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did she go...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.85,0:02:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,To make a door into this mansion takes a real big shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.91,0:02:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Look. This was made by a devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.00,0:02:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,They were apparently asking "where's Risu?"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.34,0:02:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Could it be...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.57,0:02:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The boss of the Cross-eyes...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.87,0:02:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No use...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.12,0:02:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Every door is locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.50,0:02:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.62,0:02:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Risu...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.80,0:03:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what happens, don't tell them about that man...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.76,0:03:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,"That man", huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.65,0:03:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.48,0:03:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something I want you to tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.08,0:03:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who killed me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.02,0:03:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.09,0:03:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I managed to lose the big guy, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.12,0:03:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This mansion is so vast.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.18,0:03:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Finding a single person here is almost impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.46,0:03:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Cross-marks on the eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.45,0:03:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I finally found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.40,0:03:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Risu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.52,0:03:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Risu! Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.77,0:03:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Welcome back, En!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.12,0:03:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.53,0:04:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.83,0:04:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, En?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.27,0:04:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Unforgivable...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.46,0:04:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.01,0:04:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.68,0:04:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, En!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.63,0:04:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like I was saved thanks to already having En's smoke going through my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.07,0:04:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.54,0:04:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Risu...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.00,0:04:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Please help me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.14,0:05:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who killed me was someone from the Cross-eyes, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.69,0:05:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw him just before I got killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.25,0:05:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.30,0:05:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Enjoy being a mushroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.10,0:05:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, wait! Wait, wait, wait! Risu...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.13,0:05:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? That was...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.70,0:05:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ebisu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.72,0:05:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Sniffle...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.92,0:05:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.13,0:05:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Noi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.00,0:05:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop En's rampage...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.37,0:05:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Or he'll turn us all into mushrooms!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.53,0:05:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.73,0:05:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop that, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.30,0:05:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,For real...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.31,0:05:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.32,0:05:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Nikaido? You're so late!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.66,0:05:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Caiman... Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.02,0:05:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Nikaido!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.76,0:05:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Before the magic goes through my entire body...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.52,0:06:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut this mushroom off with your knife...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.76,0:06:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Huh...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.66,0:06:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Half of your body has turned into mushrooms...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.33,0:06:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.02,0:06:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's that woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.86,0:06:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,How should we know? One of these mushrooms, probably!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.87,0:06:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That reminds me, where's Kikurage? Don't tell me she turned into a mushroom as well...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.51,0:06:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Kikurage...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.92,0:06:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad you're okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.48,0:06:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Need moisture...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.41,0:06:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,All done...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.44,0:06:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We did everything we could.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.24,0:06:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Good work. Here's some tea and daifuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.28,0:06:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.48,0:06:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The surgery went well, but that was a pretty close call.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.56,0:06:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Good thing you brought her to the hospital so fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.94,0:07:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,When I stabbed the mushroom with my knife, blood came gushing out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.21,0:07:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I panicked and used the spray I got from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.82,0:07:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I filled that can with smoke that creates those magic doors.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.41,0:07:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, Doc...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.68,0:07:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard the patched up boy came back to Hole?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.90,0:07:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.67,0:07:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,He cut this lizard's head off the other day!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.55,0:07:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently he was wearing some crazy heart-shaped mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.61,0:07:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy... Just what was he doing in Hole?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.18,0:07:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,There's sort of a connection between that guy and this hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.01,0:07:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.71,0:07:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\frz335.9\pos(1386.4,200.4)}65 Murdered
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.71,0:07:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\frz331.5\pos(866,840.267)}The\Nculprit\Nis the\Npatched\Nup boy
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.83,0:07:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a story from around ten years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.91,0:07:55.55,Title 2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,538)}"The First Smoke"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.12,0:08:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Back then the residents of Hole hadn't yet quietly accepted being practiced on like nowadays.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.91,0:08:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We were fighting back against the sorcerers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.82,0:08:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The neighborhood watch took the lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.46,0:08:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The sorcerer hunt got pretty nasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.41,0:08:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Until that man showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.59,0:08:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,His name is Shin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.93,0:08:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,His father was a human, his mother a sorcerer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.22,0:08:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that his mother was killed by the neighborhood watch right after Shin was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.19,0:08:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Shin kept his mixed blood hidden and lived quietly with his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.95,0:08:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.28,0:08:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The factory manager did not miss the black particles mixed in his blood that proved him a sorcerer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.68,0:08:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The manager told on him immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.53,0:08:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone who found a sorcerer would be rewarded with money.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.94,0:09:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It didn't take the neighborhood watch even ten minutes to arrive at the factory.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.30,0:09:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the kid! Kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.29,0:09:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.94,0:09:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Shin! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.40,0:09:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Old man...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.55,0:09:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.39,0:09:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Move it! You snitching bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.69,0:09:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,After him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.34,0:09:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.37,0:09:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Down there! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.99,0:09:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Contact the headquarters and make the posters!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.71,0:09:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it! My son's not a sorcerer!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.34,0:09:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, his mother was a sorcerer, but Shin can't use any magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.30,0:09:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,His mother was a sorcerer, you say...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.00,0:09:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, what are you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.81,0:09:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Taking out the trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.39,0:09:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit... That pig of a manager, he sold me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.13,0:09:57.52,Handwriting,,0,0,0,,{\pos(660,187.6)}This boy is a sorcerer
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.13,0:09:57.52,Handwriting,,0,0,0,,{\pos(660,854.266)}If you see him, let us know!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.13,0:09:57.52,Handwriting,,0,0,0,,{\pos(660,929.867)}Reward money available
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.13,0:09:57.52,Handwriting,,0,0,0,,{\pos(660,1021.733)}Hole Neighborhood Watch
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.93,0:10:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad and I need to get out of this town tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.82,0:10:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.37,0:10:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew you'd come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.62,0:10:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Kids are so simpleminded.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.25,0:10:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We finished cleaning up the trash...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.45,0:10:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it's just you, sorcerer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.96,0:10:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! Let's have party and burn him at the stake at the department store square tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.75,0:10:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna need a ton of beer!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.21,0:10:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take the money from this house!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.95,0:10:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Take the kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.90,0:10:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Come!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.13,0:10:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Bastard...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.62,0:11:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.63,0:11:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Just try it, brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.19,0:11:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm starting to enjoy this a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.53,0:11:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, Shin killed the three members of the neighborhood watch and ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.01,0:11:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The neighborhood watch went after him, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.16,0:11:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It just resulted in more and more corpses on their side instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.91,0:11:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Days like this continued for three months.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.88,0:11:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Then one night...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.87,0:11:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was on duty at the hospital with the Professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.69,0:11:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this? Whose voice is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.83,0:11:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's coming from the operating room.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.47,0:11:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.18,0:12:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I borrowed... Your equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.86,0:12:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you cut up your arms to search for the smoke veins?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.79,0:12:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently sorcerers who struggle to put out smoke often do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.07,0:12:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd get paid if you ratted me out to the neighborhood watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.00,0:12:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but those guys are nasty, I won't call them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.04,0:12:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And moreover, I'm really interested in your magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.51,0:12:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.59,0:12:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm researching sorcerers!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.90,0:12:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll find your smoke veins for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.59,0:12:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold still...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.01,0:12:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But I never thought I'd get to play with a living sorcerer!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.46,0:12:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Do anything weird and I'll knock you out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.96,0:12:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna get killed if the neighborhood watch finds out about this, Kasukabe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.16,0:12:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Should probably give him some antibiotics...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.46,0:12:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really fine with no anesthesia?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.23,0:12:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No need for that at this point!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.05,0:12:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, you. I understand how you feel, but you should stop killing people already.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.31,0:12:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Your father in heaven is probably really sad too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.49,0:13:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You think such lame preaching is gonna get me to stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.01,0:13:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Our family motto is "if you get hit, make sure to return the favor"!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.56,0:13:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.48,0:13:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I found the veins in both arms. With this you should be able to use magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.93,0:13:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, boy! What should we do with your chopped up arms?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.05,0:13:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Attach all of them again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.91,0:13:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I did such a stupid thing they'd never go back to how they were.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.60,0:13:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,They're just gonna rot bit-by-bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.69,0:13:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,In the world of the sorcerers...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.65,0:13:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,There must be people who can cure injuries and illnesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.62,0:13:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get them to heal me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.22,0:13:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Gyoza!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.09,0:13:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't you want some gyoza...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.88,0:13:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Gyoza... Gyoza...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.41,0:13:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.80,0:13:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H9C9C9C&\pos(897.6,156.4)}Central Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.44,0:13:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,After I'm done with some business, I'm going to the sorcerers' world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.68,0:13:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That so? If you don't mind, would you like to show us your magic once?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.56,0:13:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it. I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.18,0:14:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.71,0:14:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H9C9C9C&\pos(897.6,156.4)}Central Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.37,0:14:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't you want some gyoza...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.22,0:14:08.82,Handwriting 2,,0,0,0,,{\frz342.7\pos(1694.8,822.8)}Hungry\NBug\NGyoza
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.72,0:14:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! You thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.84,0:14:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,A few hours later...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.42,0:14:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,46 neighborhood watch members were brought to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.56,0:14:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What the hell is this? They're in pieces, but they're still alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.86,0:14:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This is magic... That boy did this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.32,0:14:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This was the "business" he was talking about...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.65,0:14:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, he did keep his promise...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.83,0:14:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,To treat those chopped up people, a magic victim ward was established in a hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.36,0:14:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The neighborhood watch disbanded after that incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.99,0:14:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody has stood up to the sorcerers since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.77,0:14:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But as expected, that guy really didn't grow up to be a decent adult at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.40,0:14:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, something like that would twist anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.82,0:14:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.98,0:15:01.44,Title,,0,0,0,,{\frz22.34\pos(827.2,868.267)}"Manhole\NElegy"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.48,0:15:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you know, Caiman?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.58,0:15:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorcerers are weak to the rain in Hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.15,0:15:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Good grief, it's raining?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.83,0:15:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Asu said he doesn't know the sorcerer who gave Caiman the lizard head...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.36,0:15:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean that just finding the guy who cast the magic on Caiman is not good enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.96,0:15:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get it. I don't get it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.24,0:15:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is troubling you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.92,0:15:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wouldn't using your magic be the fastest shortcut?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.83,0:15:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If that ends up being the only way...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.83,0:15:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.60,0:15:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Nikaido! It's time for your meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.72,0:16:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't kick the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.18,0:16:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.79,0:16:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Just now, someone was outside the window...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.84,0:16:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.98,0:16:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat these gyoza I made!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.50,0:16:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.94,0:16:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The wrapping is burnt black...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.96,0:16:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no thickener and the minced meat is tasteless and raw...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.46,0:16:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean... That they're bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.07,0:16:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you get the hospital food from the center?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.38,0:16:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Since when has Caiman been cooking?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.70,0:16:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The number of patients started to rapidly go down last month.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.72,0:16:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,One large deluxe mix pizza, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.85,0:16:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,- You're the only one hospitalized...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.09,0:16:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So we've temporarily suspended the orders from the center.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.14,0:16:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the order! That'll be 3,500 yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.01,0:16:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Recently the practice victims have been disappearing more and more in Hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.46,0:16:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,- Thanks, put it on my tab.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.69,0:16:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Mass disappearances? I wonder if it's because of the magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.56,0:16:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to that, the hospital is not doing so good lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.79,0:17:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.77,0:17:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.18,0:17:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, by the way, Caiman.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.18,0:17:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.03,0:17:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you recognize this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.07,0:17:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Nope, what's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.55,0:17:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's something like a pass high-level sorcerers receive from devils.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.69,0:17:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would Nikaido have something like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.42,0:17:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just going to tell me Nikaido is a sorcerer again!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.01,0:17:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just how it is, Caiman.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.95,0:17:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We operated on her with our own hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.43,0:17:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The bodies of sorcerers and humans are different.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.37,0:17:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Caiman?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.57,0:17:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard a scream just now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.81,0:17:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Nikaido!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.17,0:17:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Nikaido!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.75,0:17:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.40,0:17:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Nikaido!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.72,0:17:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.33,0:18:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait up! You...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.86,0:18:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.74,0:18:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That alley!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.08,0:18:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Moron! That leads to a dead end!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.21,0:18:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait up, you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.05,0:18:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Nikaido... Why isn't she resisting?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.87,0:18:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if she's sick, if it's her...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.23,0:18:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sorcerers are weak to the rain in Hole.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.93,0:18:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.08,0:18:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Squee!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.49,0:18:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Squee! Squee!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.72,0:18:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Goddamn monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.85,0:18:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this caused by the magic smoke mixing with the rainwater?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.19,0:18:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.31,0:18:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.24,0:19:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.53,0:19:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Corpses? Could they be the missing practice victims?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.85,0:19:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Squee!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.30,0:19:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.33,0:19:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.88,0:19:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not there! Why isn't it there?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.27,0:19:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,M-My black gemstone...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.07,0:19:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.16,0:19:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard, I'm gonna kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.74,0:19:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Jo-Jonson!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.14,0:19:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Squee!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.70,0:19:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hold him down, Jonson. Just like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.53,0:19:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard! What are you doing with Nikaido?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.13,0:19:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,F-For the sake of these black gemstones...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.65,0:20:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If you collect the gemstones that are inside the p-practice victims' bodies...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.78,0:20:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You can become a sorcerer...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.82,0:20:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,B-Black gemstones?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.57,0:20:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are just waste!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.64,0:20:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But for some reason this woman didn't have one...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.18,0:20:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,S-So I'm taking the one inside you... Lizard-man!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.95,0:20:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,As if I'd let you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.74,0:20:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Go fetch, Jonson!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.58,0:20:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Squee!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.79,0:20:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I saw you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.26,0:20:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That day... I came out of the manhole... And you were there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.74,0:20:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You had a human face.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.70,0:20:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You saw it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.83,0:20:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,My face before the magic was cast on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.40,0:20:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That woman was there too...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.47,0:20:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Nikaido was?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.75,0:20:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I... Wanted to become a sorcerer...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.79,0:20:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,To get away from this filthy town...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.77,0:20:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What do you mean? Did you see him?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.44,0:21:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who cast the magic on me? Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.32,0:21:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Lately, because of some baseless rumors...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.37,0:21:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The amount of youngsters who wish to become sorcerers has increased.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.46,0:21:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You could say he's another victim created by Hole's distortion.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.59,0:21:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want an umbrella?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.47,0:21:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.22,0:21:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Squee?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.97,0:23:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What we learned from the sixth curse:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.85,0:23:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,1. Shin is mixed race.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.36,0:23:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,2. Hole used to have a neighborhood watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.73,0:23:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,3. The currency in Hole is yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.24,0:23:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And what you will learn from the seventh curse...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.29,0:23:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's still a mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.54,0:23:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.84,0:23:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,DOROHEDORO

